  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Techniques:</strong> Grey <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> <em><strong>Talisman of Defilement</strong></em> &amp; <em><strong>Chakra Draining Mechanism</strong></em> <br />After using the <em>Talisman of Defilement</em>, your Puppet Tool may thin the veil between life and death further as Bonus Action, activating its <em>Chakra Draining Mechanism.</em> This affects up to two creatures within the supernatural darkness as if they where grappled. Additionally, each creature who fails their Constutition Saving Throw also reduces their maximun movement speed by half and gain 2 ranks of Exhaustion until the end of its next turn.</p><p></p>",
